$ RMAN: autobackup
@ autobackup

→ development/databases/Oracle/tools/RMAN can be configured to automatically backup the
  → development/databases/Oracle/architecture/database/files/control and
  → development/databases/Oracle/architecture/database/files/server-parameter-file.

code {
→ development/databases/Oracle/tools/RMAN/commands/configure → development/databases/Oracle/architecture/database/files/control[controlfile] autobackup on;
code }

Later:
code {
→ development/databases/Oracle/tools/RMAN/commands/restore controlfile from autobackup;
code }
